{"tid":1466701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔割，打死都唔割","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:33.000Z","uid":19183,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4a1cad093e15410623dfa126cee2fb131baa34","tid":1466701,"uid":19183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"要相信現場手足既分析<br />\n<br />\n打鬼又好，捉鬼又好，前線決定點都唔會割<br />\n<br />\n721，811加加埋埋咁多野<br />\n<br />\n邊個割邊個就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f1971dc39b153cfa6cad2eddd9469133681b72","tid":1466701,"uid":32505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"諗下今日失敗既原因係咩先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為唔夠人呀 太少人先俾班鬼帶到風向<br />\n鬼係捉唔哂 夠多人 夠冷靜 點會俾班鬼帶到風向</span></span><br />\n冇去既人自己反省下 唔好賴手足<br />\n<br />\n鬼還鬼 核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"3a8f1f6daa2f02af95b61ab180f510f1b7f797e6","tid":1466701,"uid":226974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5436ca84aa6fd7bdb87ceccda47f2e9d3665ef30","tid":1466701,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:49.000Z","msg":"唔割"},{"pid":"0c00240d04a550978c0c634890e08592869d0880","tid":1466701,"uid":51623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:50.000Z","msg":"老閪都唔割"},{"pid":"04785d9e587cf70d07b9c87b20c0f70773db0d2e","tid":1466701,"uid":38719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:53.000Z","msg":"唔割！"},{"pid":"1dff25158334126a69864b7e024aacb6d6cd9096","tid":1466701,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:56.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/